metadata.name: THORForce #1
metadata.description: The THOR Force 1 is a custom sneaker in the style of the world's first cross-chain decentralized liquidity protocol, THORChain. This sneaker is redeemable one time for the physical version which includes a custom box and accessories. Each sneaker is made by hand by Vanir Threads. Step into Asgard while supporting the community's values of decentralization, immutability, and freedom.
